Module: PROJECT STRUCTURE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Task 1: Create the Project Structure
Objective: Introduce packages, directory structure, and the SBT build system.
Concepts Covered:
    • Packaging
    • Folder structure (src/main/scala/...)
    • SBT basics
Task Description: Create the project folders exactly as shown and add an empty Main.scala.
