MODULE 2 — CASE CLASSES & DATA MODELING
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Task 2: Implement the Employee & EmployeeStats case classes
Objective: modeling real-world data using case classes.
Concepts Covered:
    • Case Class
    • Immutability
    • Typed fields
Task Description:
Create simple models inside models/Employee.scala.

MODULE 3 — TRAITS & ABSTRACTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Objective: Introduce abstraction using traits.
Concepts Covered:
    • Traits
    • Interfaces
    • Generics
Task Description:
Implement three traits: DataReader, DataWriter, and DataTransformer.

MODULE 4 — FILE I/O, PARSING & VALIDATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Task 4: Implement CsvEmployeeReader
Objective: file handling and parsing.
Concepts Covered:
    • File I/O
    • Parsing CSV
    • Option for safe parsing
    • Validation rules
Task Description:
Read employee data from a CSV file and validate it.

MODULE 5 — COLLECTIONS & FUNCTIONAL PROGRAMMING TRANSFORMATIONS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Task 5: Implement EmployeeAnalyzer Transformer
Objective: Practice grouping, mapping, filtering, and functional programming.
Concepts Covered:
    • groupBy, map, filter, sortBy
    • Higher-order functions
    • Pure transformations
Task Description:
Compute statistics per department.

